t also has in-plane switching (IPS) for nearly 178° of wide-angle viewing - perfect for enjoying movies with friends.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Dolby Atmos®</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Lenovo A7000 is the world\'s first smartphone with the all-new Dolby Atmos® - delivering a rich, immersive sound experience. Music, videos, games, and even video chats will be enhanced with audio that flows above and around you.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Unmatched Performance</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Lenovo A7000 brings flagship performance in a surprisingly affordable product. Running 8 cores of the latest ARM Cortex 53 at 1.5GHz, the MTK6752m processor along with 2GB DDR3 RAM, the A7000 can easily handle high resolution videos, latest HD games and multitask without breaking a sweat. Experience jaw-dropping graphics with ARM Mali-T760 that can scale up to 16 cores to provide stutter free gaming anywhere.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Power to go the Distance</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A7000 houses a large battery while keeping the overall design extremely sleek. This means one can stay connected for longer, watch more videos on a single charge and not be worried about running out of charge. The all-day 2900mAh battery ensures there is no stopping your entertainment. With OTG supported, you can connect USB drives (with microUSB connector) for data transfer on the go. What’s more, you can even charge other phones from the A7000.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Blazing 4G Speed</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The A7000 supports high-speed LTE (4G) networks for the fastest data connectivity, helping you reach your full enjoyment potential when browsing, watching, reading, gaming or chatting online.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Android™ 5.0, Lollipop</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">With the latest version of Android, get ready for a faster, smoother, and more powerful performance. You\'ll find it easier to stay in the loop, interact with others, and even manage battery power. You can also better safeguard your A7000 and enjoy a host of new features to make life that much sweeter.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Dual SIM</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Two phone numbers in one smartphone is great whether you\'re separating business and pleasure, travelling to a different country, or simply want to take advantage of different service providers to save money. Not available in all regions.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Rear and Front Cameras</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">With the A7000\'s 8MP auto-focus rear camera and 5MP front camera, you can take great photos &amp; selfies all day long and share them instantly.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Built-in Lenovo Apps</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Lenovo\'s built-in DOit series of apps let you and your device do more. In a few clicks, for instance, you can share data with other devices without a network, optimize device performance, prevent viruses and malware, or back up your contacts, SMS, &amp; call logs. There\'s even an app where the background graphics will change automatically to match the actual weather.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Expandable Storage</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 20px; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows